getPSDELogicNodes.name: 获取工时数
getPSDELogicNodes.sql: select IFNULL(sum(t.consumed),0) as `YEARESTIMATECNT` from zt_taskestimate t where t.ACCOUNT = ? and DATE_FORMAT(t.date,'%Y') = ?

getPSDELogicNodes.name: 获取登录数
getPSDELogicNodes.sql: select count(1) as `YEARVISITS` from zt_action t where t.actor = ? and t.action = 'login' and DATE_FORMAT(t.date,'%Y') = ?

getPSDELogicNodes.name: 获取动态数
getPSDELogicNodes.sql: select count(1)  as `YEARACTIONCNT` from zt_action t where t.actor = ?  and DATE_FORMAT(t.date,'%Y') = ?

getPSDELogicNodes.name: 获取日志数
getPSDELogicNodes.sql: select COUNT(1) as `YEARLOGCNT` from zt_taskestimate t where t.ACCOUNT = ? and DATE_FORMAT(t.date,'%Y') = ?

getAllPSDELogics.logicName: 获取产品经理相关数据
getAllPSDELogics.name: 获取产品经理相关数据

getPSDELogicNodes.name: 获取计划数
getPSDELogicNodes.sql: select count(1) as `yearplancnt` from zt_productplan t left join zt_action t2 on t2.objectID = t.id and t2.objectType = 'productplan' where LEFT(t2.date, 4) = ? and t2.actor = ? and t2.action = 'opened' and t.product <> 0

getPSDELogicNodes.name: 获取登录数
getPSDELogicNodes.sql: select count(1) as `YEARVISITS` from zt_action t where t.actor = ? and t.action = 'login' and DATE_FORMAT(t.date,'%Y') = ?

getPSDELogicNodes.name: 获取产品数
getPSDELogicNodes.sql: select count(1) as YEARPRODUCTCNT from zt_product t where ((YEAR(t.createddate) = ? and (t.createdBy =? or t.po = ? or t.QD =? or t.RD =? )) or t.id in(select t.product from zt_productplan t left join zt_action t2 on t2.objectID = t.id and t2.objectType = 'productplan' where LEFT(t2.date, 4) = ? and t2.actor = ? and t2.action = 'opened' and t.product <> 0) or t.id in (select t.product from zt_story t where t.product > 0 and t.openedBy = ? and DATE_FORMAT(t.openedDate,'%Y') = ? ))

getPSDELogicNodes.name: 获取需求数
getPSDELogicNodes.sql: select count(1) as `yearstorycnt` from zt_story t where t.product > 0 and t.openedBy = ? and DATE_FORMAT(t.openedDate,'%Y') = ?

getAllPSDELogics.name: 获取测试人员相关数据

getPSDELogicNodes.sql: select count(1) as `YEARVISITS` from zt_action t where t.actor = ? and t.action = 'login' and DATE_FORMAT(t.date,'%Y') = ?

getPSDELogicNodes.name: 获取创建bug数
getPSDELogicNodes.sql: select count(1)  as `YEARBUGCNT` from zt_bug t where t.product > 0 and t.openedBy = ?  and DATE_FORMAT(t.openedDate,'%Y') = ?

getPSDELogicNodes.name: 获取创建用例数
getPSDELogicNodes.sql: select count(1) as `YEARCASECNT` from zt_case t where t.product > 0 and t.openedBy = ? and DATE_FORMAT(t.openedDate,'%Y') = ?

getPSDELogicNodes.name: 获取动态数
getPSDELogicNodes.sql: select count(1)  as `YEARACTIONCNT` from zt_action t where t.actor = ?  and DATE_FORMAT(t.date,'%Y') = ?

getPSDELogicNodes.name: 获取标题
getPSDELogicNodes.sql: select CONCAT_WS('',?,'年工作内容统计一览表 —— ',?) as Title from dual
